'''Subnode''' was a term used to describe a living thing created in the image of its creator. [[Kud'ar Mub'at]], member of the [[Spider/Legends|arachnid]] [[Species/Legends|species]] known as the [[Assembler]]s, had many small subnodes who served him in particular fields. Such subnodes held eponymous names, such as [[Signaler]], who notified Mub'at of arrivals to the arachnoid's web.

